<div class="article-feature-image-full-width-text">
<h1 class="article-feature-image-full-width-title">New Kindness Hatching</h1>
<h4 class="article-feature-image-full-width-subtitle"><a class="contributor-link" href="https://granta.com/contributor/jesse-glazzard/">Jesse Glazzard</a> & <a class="contributor-link" href="https://granta.com/contributor/vahni-capildeo/">Anthony (Vahni) Capildeo</a></h4>
<h4 class="article-feature-image-full-width-subtitle"></h4>
</div>
</div> </div>
</div>
<div class="background-grey --no-padding">
