<div class="col-12 col-md-8 flex --direction-col --justify-content-center article-contributor-main">
<div class="article-contributor__meta-container">
<h1 class="article-contributor-section_title">Jesse Glazzard</h1>
<p class="article-contributor-section_content">Jesse Glazzard is a portrait and documentary photographer from Yorkshire, England. Since graduating from Central Saint Martins in 2019, he has been documenting spaces, friends, lovers and models.</p>
<a class="article-contributor-section_link" href="https://granta.com/jesse-glazzard">More about the author →</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="article-contributor-photo-section ">
<div class="container">
<div class="row article-contributor-photo-reverse">
<div class="col-12 col-md-8 flex --direction-col --justify-content-center article-contributor-main">
<div class="article-contributor__meta-container">
<h1 class="article-contributor-section_title">Anthony (Vahni) Capildeo</h1>
<p class="article-contributor-section_content">Anthony (Vahni) Capildeo is Writer-in-Residence at the University of York. Capildeo’s recent work includes <em>A Happiness</em> (2022) and <em>Polkadot Wounds</em> (2024).
<br><br>
<em><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Photograph © Hayley Madden</span></em></p>
<a class="article-contributor-section_link" href="https://granta.com/vahni-capildeo">More about the author →</a>
