<div class="dnd_post-card__lower-section">
<h2 class="dnd_post-card_title">
<a href="https://granta.com/introduction-significant-other/">
Introduction
</a>
</h2>
<h4 class="dnd_post-card_author">
<a class="contributor-link" href="https://granta.com/contributor/thomas-meaney/">Thomas Meaney</a>
</h4>
<p class="dnd_post-card_text">
‘There can be any number of significant others in a life. Some we know for a long time; others are meteoric: we may see them only once.’<br/><br/>The editor introduces the issue.
</p>
